### wehub.de

Hi,

this is my personal github page. My name is Werner Huber and i'm a professional mobile app developer from Munich, Germany. Because I am constantly looking for new cool stuff, I'm developing for all current platforms (iOS, Android, WP7, BlackBerry). Please feel free to fork my OpenSource projects and take a look at my cv on this page.
